@shiyuning0987 , please try to resolve Chinese with matplotlib first:  https://github.com/hupili/python-for-data-and-media-communication-gitbook/blob/master/module-matplotlib.md  

When you can use `matplotlib`'s `plt.plot` to show Chinese characters, `seaborn` should also work. Let's followup if the former half works but not the latter half.

You may want to load fonts and make sure `matplotlib` works with Chinese, before importing seaborn.
